data.description: Welcome home to this amazing property.  With over 2 acres of land and no HOA, this property has it all.  It starts with the beautiful open floor plan with tons of big beautiful windows everywhere, and continues to the yard. The kitchen features Bosch professional appliances and plenty of space to create master chef worthy dishes. The entire back yard is fenced in, which includes a covered patio, hot tub, playground, storage shed, fire pti, fully irrigated and even a private putting green.  Inside the home, you have a formal living room, formal dining room, as well as large bedrooms, crown molding, oversized baseboards, hardwood flooring, decorative doors and hardware, and huge windows. Students can attend either Peaster ISD or Poolville ISD from this home. The home is only two years new, has all the modern features, including a water softener, humidity sensor, Slimline AC, and is wired for a generator in case of a power outage. Bring your horses and enjoy this luxurious home.
